name: Void Pulse
description:
Welcome on an unending journy  some would say... 

No Worries Safy and Risko will help you from this endless pit back to her ;)

 

Aim the mouse hook one of youre friends and get a boost. The higher the score the better ! 

Wanna go slow and steady ? Safy is the best :D 

Do you feel like taking the challenge then Risiko is the one you are looking for.
